| hostScript.jsx | `/Users/imorgado/SPLICE/splice-cep/jsx/hostScript.jsx` |
| main.js | `/Users/imorgado/SPLICE/splice-cep/panel/js/main.js` |
| builder.js | `/Users/imorgado/SPLICE/splice-cep/panel/js/builder.js` |
